name: War of the Witchdoctors
description:
"Van Gogh" was the theme for this highly detailed one-week game! A simple RTS with a selection of squads to produce VS an enemy AI with four levels of difficulty. Attempt to capture control points to increase your production and at the same time become closer to achieving victory!

(Highly Recommend the README)
